<br>
Firiona Vie is the role playing server. Many folks see us only as a blue server with a different rule set. This is what most &quot;self ritous&quot; residents are trying to defend against.  Cross server trading, and the &quot;gamer&quot; mentality are symptoms of the blue servers that many came to FV to get away from.<br>
